data.value: UPDATE [OKPO] SET [CodeOKPO] = @CodeOKPO, [NameOrganization] = @NameOrganization WHERE (((@IsNull_CodeOKPO = 1 AND [CodeOKPO] IS NULL) OR ([CodeOKPO] = @Original_CodeOKPO)) AND ([CodeRecord] = @Original_CodeRecord)); SELECT CodeOKPO, NameOrganization, CodeRecord FROM OKPO WHERE (CodeRecord = @CodeRecord)
